nodes.text: Raykos was a female Human who served as a captain in the Imperial Navy of the reconstituted Sith Empire, stationed in the Imperial First Mobile Fleet during the Galactic War.
The Reputation vendor for Imperial Heroic space missions, Captain Raykos was added to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic in Game Update 1.7: Return of the Gree on February 12, 2013.
